Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君を待った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は待った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}途切れない明日も過ぎて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}立ち止まって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:39.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}振り返って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:42.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}とめどない今日を嘆き合った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}記憶だって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}永遠になんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}残らないものとおもい知って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕はずっと　掻きむしって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}心の隅っこで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}そしてどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}なくさないでよって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}高架下、過ぎる日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:07.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}後悔してんだよって　そう言い逃したあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君を待った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は待った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:13.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}途切れない明日も過ぎて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}僕は今日も掻きむしって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}忘れない傷をつけてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur5}君じゃないとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不会中断的明天也过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:39.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}回头望去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:42.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}悲叹着无止境的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}记忆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}永远什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}让我认识到那不会留下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我一直在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}在心灵的角落中哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}然而请务必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不要丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}那高架桥下度过的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:07.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}喊着「我在后悔」却走掉的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:13.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}不会中断的明天已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我今天依然在抓狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}为自己添加着无法忘记的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}没有你一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:32.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur4}僕だけが見てた君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:45.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}過去も未来も　かなしみもよろこびも全て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:55.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}オトナになるってきっと優しくなることだと信じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:22:01.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}子供の頃の僕のままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:06.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君のこと守りたいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:08.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暗闇から目覚めても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:13.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}僕を待ち受けてる彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:23.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}二人を隠したこの街に誰も知らない雪が降っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:33.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}君が僕の胸に刻まれた一番深い傷跡のようで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:48.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(0,4000)}君が笑うこの世界の歌　取り戻すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:32.26,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\blur6}只有我看到了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:45.59,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}过去 未来 悲伤 快乐 一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:55.99,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一直相信着成为大人后一定能变得温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:22:01.84,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在我现在还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:06.23,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就决定要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:08.92,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}即便在黑暗中醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:13.70,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在等待着我的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:23.85,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}藏匿着两人的这个城市下着无人所知的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:33.07,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像你在我心里刻下了最深刻的伤痕一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:48.45,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}{\fad(0,4000)}你所欢笑着的这个世界的歌 我一定会取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤沼悟 我们以杀人以及放火杀人未遂的嫌疑逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能鼓起勇气过来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要事很快就结束了 我就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会碍事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 雏月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.36,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,悟好绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是孤单一人 就算很难看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不留下后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败的话就没有下次机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的「再上映」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃点什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿了零花钱 大家一起去吃大阪烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice 悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说悟 上上周借给你的书看了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坡的《调换了的男人》那本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我还没看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不记得了 在18年前借的书…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的 回去之后看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭马上就好 稍微等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 悟 别傻站着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和加代吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 抱歉 记一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐一次电车就能到上野去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭和63年2月29日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏月加代会成为连续诱拐杀人事件最初的被害者的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第三次迎接这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟君 好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比上一次早了一天说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不能在意太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤也 那个抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你借我的书好像弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 能到教室外面聊聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书的事不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种书根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 我话先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近该怎么说呢 我见到了认真的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的悟明明对他人完全不关心却装作有这么一回事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得那样的你也很拼命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢现在的悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想知道自己内心所产生的疑问的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来 悟变成了其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就像是多了另一个人格一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现悟的变化是在悟看着雏月的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久之前就发现了雏月的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是这样保持一定距离看他人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 在那样的我的面前 你深入了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说就像「要这样做」的意识进入了悟的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在训斥着我一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为这种人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤也 雏月会被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了虐待的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我绝对会阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是出了结果就能成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为悟是讨厌雏月的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是同族厌恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经讨厌过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是反过来也有吸引着我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多少少能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 贤也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着水桶到走廊去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的伙伴真是不走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广美 贤也 能和雏月在幼儿园等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天3月1日只要不让雏月单独呆在公园就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是3月2日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日派对那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要勇气哥有不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气哥的爸爸的房间在一楼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近马路那边的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我只是在想晚上会不会很吵之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 还剩一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气哥 你和雏月加代见过了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近她在和我们那伙一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得这几天都不见她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！ 加代那是最棒的结果啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气哥第一次在我面前说方言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再 再见 悟君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照那样子来看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是被偶然见到他与雏月碰面的真犯利用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇气哥 等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会阻止事件的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏月 贤也 广美？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟三个人也没法玩黑白棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是在3月2日之前避开这种突然的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就没办法预测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 雏月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将3月1日设为和上回一样度过的X日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据今天之后的行动来改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去学校取遗留物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么急吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关它自不自然 不是在意这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来今晚一晚警察就能为不在场证明作证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.27,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.75,Default02,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要排除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把那家伙从雏月的眼前排除掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你不在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点吧 悟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更麻烦的是你因为制裁而离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 我在这两天一直跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了救雏月很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 贤也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我今天无论如何都觉得雏月很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟你在来这里之前也做了些不得了的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是另一件事 我想把警察叫到那去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤也 希望你能帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止她母亲的虐待 我们惊动警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟 这可能会引起大骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有考虑过结局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤也 这是我现在才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些我之后再考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算变成事件也没关系 在中途被发现也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我被制裁也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有什么结局都比雏月的死要好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要准备悟你被逮捕的结局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母亲的话一定会说「做得好」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 来干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去送雏月了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次记得穿夹克和劳动手套了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}雏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}藤沼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 现在开始我把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拐走可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我只能想到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没人在用的巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说曾是泉水小的冰球部的部室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是去年引入了另一辆巴士 这里成了库房
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开暖炉之前把换气口打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要贴得太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常棒的藏身处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想住在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这里没有浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在大房子里也不代表就是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是得回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 雏月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会回去一趟 半夜再过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会敲3次门的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 悟 贤也君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着道谢 我们是朋友嘛 加代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会保护加代的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还加代呢 你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤也不也叫人家加代…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不方便叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她「雏」会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「加代」就让悟你来叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了用不着道谢 而且接下来才叫辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这次的事露馅了 你可要装作不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够迟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 稍微绕了点路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非雏月的妈妈打电话来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我明天会很早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上就不用起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐吃这个就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜的杯面很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的半夜还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了夏天 我和贤也他们计划好要去露营的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加代也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好我过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在泉水小的人来上学之前出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加代…迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午的放送时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位同学在吃饭之前都洗手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前还没有任何动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏月的母亲已经报警了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还不会找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次的3月2号雏月在21点之前回到了家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到母亲和母亲的男朋友施暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23点之前雏月从关着她的库房中失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在3号0点30分雏月的母亲给我母亲打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在3号日出前犯人将雏月杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次除了雏月和我们之外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有雏月的母亲以及犯人的行动会有很大的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方都是未知的领域了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是美琴小学的教师八代学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得对和还有修保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说广美 很抱歉把你给卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎样的形式 有人愿意依靠我就很高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正在家八点前都没人在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加代也抱歉啊 把你关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么开心还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能鼓起勇气过来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上我会到加代家去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼她母亲报警吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我基本上明白了 可结尾要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 我会好好负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是我提出来的 而大家都是在协助我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人可以指责我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个盲点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家的路上 贤也说「悟也没有想到这个吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对回答了「嗯」的我这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「对我来说英雄就是这样的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是悟吗
